Deseo contar el nmero de observaciones de cada nivel de la varible Type

  • Documentacion count
count(stores, Type, sort = TRUE)

## 1    A 22

Promedio de tamao por Type

stores %>%
  group_by(Type) %>%
  summarize(PromSize = mean(Size))
## # A tibble: 3  2
##   Type  PromSize
##   <chr>    <dbl>
## 1 A      177248.
## 2 B      101191.
## 3 C       40542.

Grafico

stores %>%
  group_by(Type) %>%
  summarize(PromSize = mean(Size)) %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = Type, y = PromSize)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", fill = "blue") +
  labs(x="Tipo",y= "Promedio Size")  +              
  #ylim(c(0,300)) +
  ggtitle("Diagrama de barras")  +
  geom_text(aes(label = round(PromSize,2)), vjust = -0.3) +
  facet_wrap(~"Variable Size")
